item.title: CVE-2021-20836|2024-08-03T17:53:22.875Z -- omron%20corporation -- omron%20cx-supervisor
item.description: Out-of-bounds read vulnerability in CX-Supervisor v4.0.0.13 and v4.0.0.16 allows an attacker with administrative privileges to cause information disclosure and/or arbitrary code execution by opening a specially crafted SCS project files.
